INSERT INTO `wp_2_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2015-12-30 21:08:42','2015-12-30 21:08:42','The big idea is that failing is not just okay, it can be conducive to future success if you <strong>1) learn from it</strong> and <strong>2) use what you\'ve learned in future ventures.</strong> <strong>Use systems</strong>, not goals, because every day you apply the system you will feel accomplished. For example, focus on \"exercising daily\" instead of \"losing 10 pounds\". Successful things usually start off as successes. <strong>Learn business skills, communication skills, etc., </strong>because each skill you master doubles your odds of success, dress well, and set a routine to ensure happiness.','How to Fail at Almost Everything and Still Win Big: Kind of the Story of My Life','','publish','open','open','','how-to-fail-at-almost-everything-win-big','','','2015-12-31 02:43:30','2015-12-31 02:43:30','',0,'http://actionsteps.shipordeliver.com/?p=1',0,'post','',1),(2,1,'2015-12-30 21:08:42','2015-12-30 21:08:42','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://actionsteps.shipordeliver.com/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','publish','open','open','','sample-page','','','2015-12-30 21:08:42','2015-12-30 21:08:42','',0,'http://actionsteps.shipordeliver.com/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(4,1,'2015-12-31 00:52:48','2015-12-31 00:52:48','','cheap_diagonal_fabric','','inherit','open','open','','cheap_diagonal_fabric','','','2015-12-31 00:52:48','2015-12-31 00:52:48','',0,'http://actionsteps.shipordeliver.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/12/cheap_diagonal_fabric.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(5,1,'2015-12-31 00:59:23','2015-12-31 00:59:23','','concrete_seamless','','inherit','open','open','','concrete_seamless','','','2015-12-31 00:59:23','2015-12-31 00:59:23','',0,'http://actionsteps.shipordeliver.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/12/concrete_seamless.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(6,1,'2015-12-31 01:36:38','2015-12-31 01:36:38','','Drawing','','inherit','open','open','','drawing','','','2015-12-31 01:36:38','2015-12-31 01:36:38','',0,'http://actionsteps.shipordeliver.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/12/Drawing.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(7,1,'2015-12-31 01:49:06','2015-12-31 01:49:06','','Drawing','','inherit','open','open','','drawing-2','','','2015-12-31 01:49:06','2015-12-31 01:49:06','',0,'http://actionsteps.shipordeliver.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/12/Drawing1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(8,1,'2015-12-31 02:42:47','2015-12-31 02:42:47','The big idea is that failing is not just okay, it can be conducive to future success if you <strong>1) learn from it</strong> and <strong>2) use what you\'ve learned in future ventures.</strong> <strong>Use systems</strong>, not goals, because every day you apply the system you will feel accomplished. For example, focus on \"exercising daily\" instead of \"losing 10 pounds\". Each skill you master doubles your odds of success, dress well, and set a routine to ensure happiness.','How to Fail at Almost Everything and Still Win Big: Kind of the Story of My Life','','inherit','open','open','','1-autosave-v