rofessionals</strong></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>2012 - 2014</h2>\r\n<strong>Simple Task LLC</strong> - I was employed as a front-end developer and junior Project Manager at a devshop for about a little over a year. I went in knowing raw HTML and CSS, and was thrown into the world of software development by building interfaces for eCommerce sites and business systems.\r\n\r\nI learned HTML, CSS, Javascript, PHP, and Python during my time here.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>CodeAcademy</b>\r\n\r\n100% Python track\r\n\r\n100% Javascript track','My Curriculum','','draft','open','open','','my-curriculum','','','2015-08-03 02:50:28','2015-08-03 02:50:28','',0,'http://shipordeliver.com/?page_id=3001',0,'page','',0),(3002,1,'2015-03-12 16:09:27','2015-03-12 16:09:27','&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>MITx: </b>\r\n\r\nIntroduction to Computational Thinking and Data Science\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>CodeAcademy</b>\r\n\r\nPython track\r\n\r\nJavascript track','Start Here | Curriculum','','inherit','open','open','','3001-revision-v1','','','2015-03-12 16:09:27','2015-03-12 16:09:27','',3001,'http://shipordeliver.com/3001-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(3003,1,'2015-03-12 16:14:30','2015-03-12 16:14:30','&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>Tealeaf Academy:</b>\r\n\r\nMon, Wed, Fri\r\n\r\n<b>MITx: </b>\r\n\r\nIntroduction to Computational Thinking and Data Science\r\n\r\nTues, Thurs, Sat\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>CodeAcademy</b>\r\n\r\nPython track\r\n\r\nJavascript track','Start Here | Curriculum','','inherit','open','open','','3001-revision-v1','','','2015-03-12 16:14:30','2015-03-12 16:14:30','',3001,'http://shipordeliver.com/3001-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(3004,1,'2015-03-14 18:04:14','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Learning Is Not Linear','','draft','open','open','','','','','2015-03-14 18:04:14','2015-03-14 18:04:14','',0,'http://shipordeliver.com/?p=3004',0,'post','',0),(3005,1,'2015-03-14 18:04:14','2015-03-14 18:04:14','','Learning Is Not Linear','','inherit','open','open','','3004-revision-v1','