s, and are ultimately out of one\'s control, are essential things when dealing with anything. This is an obvious one.\r\n\r\n<b>Being Patient</b> - contrary to popular belief, doubling or tripling one\'s money in the markets is a rare feat. It\'s necessary to maintain a mental horizon of years or decades to achieve real wealth.','Why Trading Stocks is Good for the Mind','','inherit','open','open','','3253-revision-v1','','','2016-08-02 13:32:12','2016-08-02 13:32:12','',3253,'http://shipordeliver.com/3253-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
